A concern that I have with the team (can include yourself as a team member):
A pending and unaddressed, as of now, concern that I ponder about is how we will be able to effectively communicate with each other and collaborate when parts of this assignment are to be done outside of the class(room) environment.



How I plan on solving this problem:
I’m thinking a group chat on a chatting platform online will enable us to replicate the discussions and feedback that is bounced back and forth between us, as a group, in a physical setting.

